data.description: With 3 cozy bedrooms, this home is the epitome of comfort & versatility. The 2 baths offer both functionality & style to enhance your daily routine. Beyond the threshold awaits a spacious backyard, an oasis of possibilities for relaxation, play & entertaining. Summer barbecues or cozy evenings under the stars. Whether you're starting a new chapter in your life or seeking a savvy investment opportunity, this property is an ideal choice. It's the perfect canvas for your personal touch or a turnkey solution for the astute investor. Conveniently located in Cleburne, you'll enjoy easy access to local shopping, dining & entertaining, along with schools, and parks. This residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle waiting to be embraced. Don't miss the chance to make this updated and inviting property your own. Schedule a showing today and let the journey to your new home in Cleburne begin!
